    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/3a8817527000d95af4dfce7befa96615.poster.avif?t=1681183623\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/3a8817527000d95af4dfce7befa96615.webm?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/3a8817527000d95af4dfce7befa96615.mp4?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>你还记得这里的人死后他们说什么吗？<br>他们 &quot;回家 &quot;了。<br>他们在温暖的家中与他们的亲人团聚，在来世......。<br>就像现在的妈妈和爸爸。我想念他们。我想念我们温暖的家。<br>但我不希望我们两个人都死了才能到那里。<br>至少这一次，我想要一个温暖的家庭之夜。<br>而不是在早上只剩下一堆冰冷的钱。<br>你能做到这一点吗，兄弟？就一次？</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >信息</h2><br><strong>Rendezvous: Shadows of the Past</strong>是Pendopo工作室即将推出的2.5D赛博-诺尔像素艺术动作拼图冒险游戏的序幕。这场免费的冒险发生在海湾市，跟随保安Setyo开始他平凡工作的另一天--直到一张熟悉的面孔从他的过去重新出现。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 功能介绍 </h2><br><strong>图形</strong><br>在一个2.5D的世界中，2D手绘像素艺术的惊人组合，与动态照明和绽放等现代效果相融合，为你周围的城市带来深度和生命。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/e0d1472c28fc1102d7fee76e952b961b.poster.avif?t=1681183623\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/e0d1472c28fc1102d7fee76e952b961b.webm?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/e0d1472c28fc1102d7fee76e952b961b.mp4?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>探索</strong><br>多条路径通向物品、感兴趣的物体和工具，帮助你找到你的妹妹--沿途还有许多秘密<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/41bb911e8153ff47ca301c985812780a.poster.avif?t=1681183623\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/41bb911e8153ff47ca301c985812780a.webm?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/41bb911e8153ff47ca301c985812780a.mp4?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>拼图</strong><br>收集线索并利用你所知道的一切来解决阻碍你获得救赎的挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/030fe10716603079f6ca50da4cd8dce9.poster.avif?t=1681183623\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/030fe10716603079f6ca50da4cd8dce9.webm?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/030fe10716603079f6ca50da4cd8dce9.mp4?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>隐身和战斗</strong><br>对于不喜欢冒险的人来说，可以在威胁面前偷偷摸摸......或者直接用现有的（有时是临时的）武器与他们对抗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/5ca05fdf978b229e2042fed84f4108c2.poster.avif?t=1681183623\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/5ca05fdf978b229e2042fed84f4108c2.webm?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825480/extras/5ca05fdf978b229e2042fed84f4108c2.mp4?t=1681183623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
